"Dear users:
Thank you for using Konka mobile phone! In order to facilitate us to provide you with satisfactory after-sales service, please complete mobile phone registration;This registration will only result in a normal SMS fee, charged by the carrier that provides the communication service for your phone. In order to improve your experience, Konka needs to make statistics on the use of mobile phone functions, including your device identification data (IMEI, ESN, MEID and SN), hardware configuration data, user behavior data, and error log data.By analyzing the statistical data, the operating system is continuously improved Inspection, operation performance, improvement function design, etc. When it comes to statistics, we only count the system itself,not refer to your personal privacy data, and the collected and processed user data cannot be used to identify and track your personal identity. In the data statistics may generate the Internet traffic, please consult the local operators for the data traffic expense."
"Thanks for your support! Konka Communications Technology Co.,Ltd."
